NAME
  aspect43 - adjusts image files in the current directory to 4:3 aspect ratio
SYNOPSIS
  aspect43
DESCRIPTION
  aspect43 converts every image file of a variety of formats 
  (tga, bmp, png, gif, jpeg)
  in the current working directory to a 640x480 png
  image.
  Conversion is performed using ImageMagick(1)'s convert(1) utility.
  The output files are placed into a 'out' subfolder, 
  which is created if needed.
SEE ALSO
  ImageMagick(1), convert(1)
AUTHOR
  Ryan Armstrong <software@zerker.ca>
